{"title":"[Markdown]语法","date":"2023-04-08T00:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Apr 8, 2023","L":"04/08/2023","MM-DD":"04-08"},"link":"2023/04/08/[Markdown]语法","comments":true,"categories":["Markdwon"],"updated":"2023-04-08T00:00:00.000Z","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>markdown介绍， 基本语法，typora中编写markdown的方式</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"markdown介绍\">Markdown介绍<a title=\"#markdown介绍\" href=\"#markdown介绍\"></a></h2>\n<p><strong>Markdown</strong>是一种轻量级标记语言, 旨在于成为一种<strong>易读易写</strong>书写格式, <strong>兼容HTML</strong>, 广泛应用于文档编写, 已有越来越多的网站支持Markdwon.</p>\n<h2 id=\"markdown编辑器\">Markdown编辑器<a title=\"#markdown编辑器\" href=\"#markdown编辑器\"></a></h2>\n<p>推荐VSCode Obsdian 和 Typora, 这里介绍<a href=\"https://typora.io/\" target=\"_blank\">Typora</a>, 现已收费.</p>\n<h3 id=\"编辑模式\">编辑模式<a title=\"#编辑模式\" href=\"#编辑模式\"></a></h3>\n<p>typora是<strong>Seamless Live Preview</strong>, 在普通编辑模式下输入markdown语法会实时预览, 但我一般不在这个模式下书写, 因为自动生成会妨碍我们输入.<br>\n<code>ctrl+/</code>切换到源代码模式, 开始书写真正的Markdown.</p>\n<h3 id=\"typora常用快捷键\">Typora常用快捷键<a title=\"#typora常用快捷键\" href=\"#typora常用快捷键\"></a></h3>\n<div class=\"φbq\"><div class=\"φbs\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"padding:0\"></th>\n<th style=\"padding:0\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>ctrl /</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">切换编辑模式</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>shift F12</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">开发者工具</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>ctrl shift L</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">显示/隐藏侧边栏</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><p><strong>建议记住上面三个</strong></p>\n<div class=\"φbq\"><div class=\"φbs\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"padding:0\"></th>\n<th style=\"padding:0\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>ctrl shift S</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">另存为</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>ctrl F</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">查找</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>ctrl P</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">查找文档</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>ctrl N</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">新建文件</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>ctrl shift N</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">新建面板</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><h2 id=\"markdown语法\">Markdown语法<a title=\"#markdown语法\" href=\"#markdown语法\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"内嵌html\">内嵌HTML<a title=\"#内嵌html\" href=\"#内嵌html\"></a></h3>\n<p>可以直接写HTML, Markdown实际上是对HTML的封装, <code>shift F12</code>打开开发者工具, 我们能看见Markdown的HTML实现</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/s1acr/PicGoLib@main/Typora/202304290056528.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"区段元素(span-elements)\">区段元素(span elements)<a title=\"#区段元素(span-elements)\" href=\"#区段元素(span-elements)\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"加粗-斜体-代码-删除\">加粗 斜体 代码 删除<a title=\"#加粗-斜体-代码-删除\" href=\"#加粗-斜体-代码-删除\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"strong\">**strong**</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"emphasis\">*italic*</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"code\">`code`</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">~~del~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>strong</strong><br>\n<em>italic</em><br>\n<code>code</code><br>\n<s>del</s></p>\n<h4 id=\"链接\">链接<a title=\"#链接\" href=\"#链接\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[<span class=\"string\">title</span>](<span class=\"link\">href</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">[<span class=\"string\">link to baidu</span>](<span class=\"link\">https://www.baidu.com</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.baidu.com\" target=\"_blank\">link to baidu</a></p>\n<p>href属性可以设置为<strong>锚点链接</strong>, 这样我们能实现文内跳转</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[<span class=\"string\">点击跳转到参考</span>](<span class=\"link\">#ref</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span> <span class=\"attr\">id</span> = <span class=\"string\">&quot;ref&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><span class=\"strong\">**参考:**</span><span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><a href=\"#ref\">点击跳转到参考</a></p>\n<p><strong>自动跳转链接</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-xml\">&lt;https://www.baidu.com&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.baidu.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.baidu.com</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"脚注和注释\">脚注和注释<a title=\"#脚注和注释\" href=\"#脚注和注释\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">footnote [ ^1]</span><br><span class=\"line\">[<span class=\"symbol\">^1</span>]: <span class=\"link\">expaination</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>点击前往注释<br>\n官方文档<a href=\"%5B%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%5D(https://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax)\">^1</a><br>\nwiki百科<a href=\"%5Bwiki%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91%5D(https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Markdown)\">^2</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"图片\">图片<a title=\"#图片\" href=\"#图片\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">![<span class=\"string\">Alt text</span>](<span class=\"link\">path</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"../pics/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/illust_99872790_20230129_132735-16814946294191.jpg\" alt=\"illust_99872790_20230129_132735\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"区块元素(block-elements)\">区块元素(block elements)<a title=\"#区块元素(block-elements)\" href=\"#区块元素(block-elements)\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"标题\">标题<a title=\"#标题\" href=\"#标题\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\"># h1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">### h3</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">###### h6</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"引用\">引用<a title=\"#引用\" href=\"#引用\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"quote\">&gt; content</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"quote\">&gt; &gt; nest content</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>支持嵌套</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>顾城 一代人</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>我知道这世界满是肮脏。<br>\n我知道要自私自利一样才能生活上活的更好。<br>\n我知道人心中始终涌动着恶意，哪怕我自己内心也是。<br>\n但我就是无法放弃善意与道德。<br>\n因为冰冷的黑暗始终不会让我有归属感，不让让我内心获得安宁。<br>\n因为只有善意与温暖会让我内心得到我最想要的平静。<br>\n所以即使明知这一切是如此绝望，我仍然在寻找善的理想乡。<br>\n黑暗给了我黑色的眼睛，我却用它寻找光明。<br>\n我是一只该在黑夜里飞舞的蛾子，却永远无法抵挡住那火光的诱惑，以至于被烧成了灰烬</p>\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"列表\">列表<a title=\"#列表\" href=\"#列表\"></a></h4>\n<p><strong>无序</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// * - + </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"bullet\">*</span> todo<span class=\"emphasis\">_1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"emphasis\">* todo_</span>2</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"bullet\">*</span> todo<span class=\"emphasis\">_3</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>todo_1</li>\n<li>todo_2</li>\n<li>todo_3</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>有序</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"bullet\">1.</span> todo<span class=\"emphasis\">_1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"emphasis\">2. todo_</span>2</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"bullet\">3.</span> todo<span class=\"emphasis\">_3</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"代码块\">代码块<a title=\"#代码块\" href=\"#代码块\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 没有空格</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"code\">` `</span>`[language]</span><br><span class=\"line\"> code</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"code\">` `</span>`</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"表格\">表格<a title=\"#表格\" href=\"#表格\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">column<span class=\"emphasis\">_1 | column_</span>2 | column<span class=\"emphasis\">_3</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"emphasis\">:--- | :---: | ---:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"emphasis\">left | center | right</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<div class=\"φbq\"><div class=\"φbs\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:left\">column_1</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">column_2</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:right\">column_3</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">left</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">center</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right\">right</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><h3 id=\"转义字符\">转义字符<a title=\"#转义字符\" href=\"#转义字符\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">\t\\开头的转义字符</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\\   backslash</span><br><span class=\"line\">`   backtick</span><br><span class=\"line\">*   asterisk</span><br><span class=\"line\">_   underscore</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;&#125;  curly braces</span><br><span class=\"line\">[]  square brackets</span><br><span class=\"line\">()  parentheses</span><br><span class=\"line\">#   hash mark</span><br><span class=\"line\">+   plus sign</span><br><span class=\"line\">-   minus sign (hyphen)</span><br><span class=\"line\">.   dot</span><br><span class=\"line\">!   exclamation mark</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>或者用HTML中的转义字符:</strong></p>\n<p>HTML特殊符号一览表:<br>\n<a href=\"http://limi.lfszk.com/aspx/tool/htmlchar/?tool_id=24\" target=\"_blank\">http://limi.lfszk.com/aspx/tool/htmlchar/?tool_id=24</a></p>\n<p><span id = \"ref\"><strong>参考:</strong></span></p>\n","prev":{"title":"[Mermaid一]Flowchart","link":"2023/04/10/[Mermaid一]Flowchart"},"next":{"title":"地下室","link":"2023/04/07/地下室"},"plink":"https://s1acr.github.io/2023/04/08/[Markdown]语法/","toc":[{"id":"markdown介绍","title":"Markdown介绍","index":"1"},{"id":"markdown编辑器","title":"Markdown编辑器","index":"2","children":[{"id":"编辑模式","title":"编辑模式","index":"2.1"},{"id":"typora常用快捷键","title":"Typora常用快捷键","index":"2.2"}]},{"id":"markdown语法","title":"Markdown语法","index":"3","children":[{"id":"内嵌html","title":"内嵌HTML","index":"3.1"},{"id":"区段元素(span-elements)","title":"区段元素(span elements)","index":"3.2","children":[{"id":"加粗-斜体-代码-删除","title":"加粗 斜体 代码 删除","index":"3.2.1"},{"id":"链接","title":"链接","index":"3.2.2"},{"id":"脚注和注释","title":"脚注和注释","index":"3.2.3"},{"id":"图片","title":"图片","index":"3.2.4"}]},{"id":"区块元素(block-elements)","title":"区块元素(block elements)","index":"3.3","children":[{"id":"标题","title":"标题","index":"3.3.1"},{"id":"引用","title":"引用","index":"3.3.2"},{"id":"列表","title":"列表","index":"3.3.3"},{"id":"代码块","title":"代码块","index":"3.3.4"},{"id":"表格","title":"表格","index":"3.3.5"}]},{"id":"转义字符","title":"转义字符","index":"3.4"}]}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"slacr_","license":"<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src = \"/lib/cc-by-nc-sa.svg\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>","published":"April 8, 2023","updated":"April 8, 2023"},"reading_time":"778 words in 5 min"}